value.string: To save the amendment changes by providing the Effective date.
1. Formating the Effective date from yyyy-mm-dd  to dd/mm/yy formate.
2. Clck on save->enter effective date->click ok.

3. Warning pop up is handled.
Pop up appears if effective date is invalid.
